Class ChangeQueryCriteria

java.lang.Object
  change.ChangeQueryCriteria

public class ChangeQueryCriteria
extends java.lang.Object

Value object representing the properties of a ChangeLog query. The query can be made for changes of 1 or more files, during a specific interval, or for all the file and group changes in a group.
